Title: agent_prometheus: fixing piggyback host names
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1615963076
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.0.0p2

In the previous version, some piggyback hosts generated by the
Prometheus special agent were prepended by underscores. This werk
fixes the name formatting to remove these characters.
